Line29.83542: We spotted others in the hills before this one tore from the earth.
Line27.83542: It seems to be drawn to the risen remains.
Line25.83542: If your aim is to follow them, you won't get far with all this fog.
Line17.83542: They headed toward Solitude, the top of the hill. The sound of Airidah’s talharpa carried with the wind, and then this madness began.
Line1.83542: Airidah came through with a horned woman. Not her normal company, to be sure.
